  <brief_title>A Thorough ECG Study in Subjects With Acne Vulgaris Treated With SB204</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Double-dummy, Randomized, 4-period Crossover Study to Define the ECG Effects of SB204 Using a Clinical and Supratherapeutic Dose Compared With Placebo and Moxifloxacin in Subjects With Acne Vulgaris: A Thorough ECG STudy</official_title>
